*2012：《[[魔鬼命令：轟天決戰|魔鬼命令：轟天決戰]]》-導演，編劇，剪輯師<ref name=paris>{{cite web|last=Antosca|first=Nick|title=Masterpiece Theatre: Universal Soldier: Day of Reckoning|url=http://www.theparisreview.org/blog/tag/john-hyams/|publisher=Paris Review|accessdate=2013-03-24|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414080913/https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/tag/john-hyams/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
